column2: select   s.specobjID, s.bestobjID, s.firstrelease, s.survey, s.sourcetype, s.class,   gal.ra, gal.raErr, gal.dec, gal.decErr, s.z, s.zErr,   gal.r, gal.i, gal.g, gal.dered_r, gal.dered_i, gal.dered_g, gal.psfMag_r, gal.petroMag_r, gal.extinction_r, gal.petroR5#_r INTO mydb.LRG_CUTI&II FROM Galaxy AS gal   JOIN SpecObj AS s ON gal.onjID = s.bestobjID  WHERE ( ( flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) | dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) | dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) > #    and ( flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) | dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) | dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) != dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)    and ( flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) | dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) = #    and gal.petroMag_i > #    and (gal.petroMag_r > # or gal.petroR5#_r > #)    and (gal.petroMag_r > # and gal.g > # and gal.r > # and gal.i > #)    and ( (gal.petroMag_r-gal.extinction_r) < #      and (gal.petroMag_r - gal.extinction_r < (# + (#/#) * (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r) + # * (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i) - # * #) )      and ( (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i - (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r)/# - #) < #)      and ( (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i - (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r)/# - #) > #)      and ( (gal.petroMag_r - gal.extinction_r + # * LOG1#(# * # * gal.petroR5#_r * gal.petroR5#_r)) < #) )    or ( (gal.petroMag_r - gal.extinction_r < #)      and ( (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i - (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r)/# - #) > (# - # * (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r)) )      and ( (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r) > (# + # * (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i)) ) )    and ( (gal.petroMag_r - gal.extinction_r + # * LOG1#(# * # * gal.petroR5#_r * gal.petroR5#_r) ) < # ) )
